<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">דּמה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
דּמה / dâmâh / daw-maw'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''דּמה'''

# To compare; by implication to resemble, liken, consider: - compare, devise, (be) like (-n), mean, think, use similitudes.

